
This project is about a shop of sports quiptment management.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

fronted--> as fronted he i use react,tailwind ,daisy ui and redux for local state
management and for server state management RTk query.There are also aso library for animation of Home page. 
For the payment here are used Stripe .

backed-->express, mongodb,mongoose and eslint prettier for format and code error checking.

-----------------------------------all pages--------------------------------------------------

All product page --> There are category, brand ,price,rating etc every product that help you 

to reach your product. you can search by name,brand,category. here are also query you can query

by brand ,category,rating,price .Here are also short by ascending and decending order.in the bottom 

you can see the pagination.


single page-->    in the all product page ,you can see view details of every product of card .To click 
this you will go in single page.Here you can see all things about the product.you can add to card here to buy 
product at first step.


Cart--> from the single from you will go in Cart page.Here you can increase and decrease in your product and also

you can see the calculation of you shopping.

checkout page---> From the cart you can go into the checkout page , here you have to provide  some information about 
the user.then make payment about with visa card and cash on delivery and the product quantity will the reduce from the 
actual quantity.

about ---> here you can see some information about our company.our misson and vison .our team member,location and contract 
